# Sync README After Code Changes

After completing code changes, review `README.md` and update it if any of the following have changed:

- Project setup or installation steps
- Available scripts or commands
- Configuration options or environment variables
- Project structure or architecture
- Features or functionality
- API endpoints or usage examples
- Dependencies (added, removed, or updated)

Only update sections that are actually affected by the code change. Do not rewrite unrelated parts of the README.
